16:51.897 --> 16:55.061
But God says, I will be happy to.

16:55.081 --> 16:56.944
Do you realize God's happy to show you his glory?

16:57.545 --> 16:58.546
He's happy to.

16:58.818 --> 17:04.131
to reveal himself to us in his presence.

17:04.151 --> 17:08.120
I think that's such a, God is happy to show you who he is.

17:09.083 --> 17:17.202
So when Moses asks that, God says, okay, you can't see my face, that's the only thing you can't do, but I'm gonna pass by.

17:17.474 --> 17:26.543
And when I pass by, you'll be able to see my glory, and I'm gonna cover you in a rock, so with my hand, so when I go by, you'll see the afterglow of my glory.

17:26.803 --> 17:28.865
But as God passes by, what happens?

17:29.286 --> 17:34.591
There is a shout, the Lord gracious and compassionate.

17:35.812 --> 17:41.058
Slow to anger, listen to this, abounding in loving kindness or goodness.

17:43.200 --> 17:44.241
What's God's glory?

17:44.321 --> 17:45.362
How does God

17:45.634 --> 17:46.716
see His glory.

17:46.976 --> 17:51.745
He sees His glory as His loving kindness and His goodness extended to people.

17:53.227 --> 17:54.069
Isn't that beautiful?

17:55.491 --> 18:00.620
That should tell you right there, God delights in doing good to people.

18:00.640 --> 18:06.290
What happens though, a lot of people put roadblocks in their life and when a person walks

18:06.370 --> 18:16.846
in unrighteousness when they walk in impurity, when they walk in unbelief, when they walk in selfishness, when they walk in the flesh, when they believe the lie of the enemy.

18:17.227 --> 18:29.906
What happens is it diminishes by their own action, the ability of God to work in their life to the degree he would want to.

18:32.514 --> 18:37.260
God wants to work in your life in ways you can't begin to imagine he is good.

18:38.041 --> 18:39.543
Give you three scriptures and we'll close here.

18:40.745 --> 18:44.049
Give thanks to the Lord for he is good.

18:44.289 --> 18:44.790
Watch this.

18:45.471 --> 18:48.675
His love endures forever.

18:49.536 --> 18:50.037
Wow.

18:51.198 --> 18:55.124
He's good and he's good forever.

18:55.164 --> 18:57.527
The demonstration of his love is forever.

18:58.748 --> 19:00.050
Psalm 34 verse eight.

19:01.058 --> 19:04.964
Taste and see that the Lord is good.

